channel.description:
Hey all. I have this project that I have been playing around with for a while. I think I have an idea of how I would like the chorus to go and I have bits and pieces of other parts, but I’ve been busy working on some other projects at the moment and I have gotten a bit stuck. Looking for someone to collaborate with me on this track potentially. Give it a listen and let me know who would be interested.
